  "2133830": {
    "name": "破碎怪谈：恶意取关",
    "steam_appid": 2133830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/a2ba51902e7e6af36880f18bd4ad95ac.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/b05364d444d71e790ceb4070fe75d707.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/9faf8f62a730ee02d8b7676e3ec845b6.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/9faf8f62a730ee02d8b7676e3ec845b6.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/9faf8f62a730ee02d8b7676e3ec845b6.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《破碎怪谈：恶意取关》中，你将深入安妮的内心世界，经历她的恐怖之旅。她被困在一个噩梦般的世界里，周围游荡着象征她创伤的恐怖生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务是帮助安妮逃脱这些噩梦般的追踪者，同时揭开隐藏在黑暗中的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/64e6d06aea78385995cf9e635abfffae.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/64e6d06aea78385995cf9e635abfffae.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/64e6d06aea78385995cf9e635abfffae.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/94cad725e04912561e63499d4ad23eaf.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/14a16e431874a15d3d58172044c33068.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/14a16e431874a15d3d58172044c33068.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/14a16e431874a15d3d58172044c33068.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一个决定都会影响故事的发展，带来多个可能的结局。你将面对艰难的选择，每一个决定都将深刻影响安妮的命运和她周围的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择帮助安妮面对她的内心恐惧，或是让她逃避现实的痛苦。这些选择不仅会改变故事的走向，还会解锁不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/6e68d961c1ea52468e9e1f6239698da9.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/6e68d961c1ea52468e9e1f6239698da9.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/6e68d961c1ea52468e9e1f6239698da9.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/19c9c22f5a856878bca09b890cf4ed38.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/3ad727ee2f1d463c27192e786b3960f3.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/3ad727ee2f1d463c27192e786b3960f3.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/3ad727ee2f1d463c27192e786b3960f3.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中充满了象征安妮创伤的怪物，这些生物不仅令人毛骨悚然，还代表了她内心最深处的痛苦和恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将直面这些恐怖的怪物，在紧张与惊悚中挣扎求生。它们无处不在，时刻威胁着你的安全，每一个角落都可能隐藏着致命的危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/46c442117d5577a5cddbc49bd098635c.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/46c442117d5577a5cddbc49bd098635c.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/46c442117d5577a5cddbc49bd098635c.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上《破碎怪谈：恶意取关》的旅程，面对内心的恐惧，揭开隐藏的秘密，体验前所未有的超现实恐怖冒险。准备好迎接这场心跳加速的恐怖之旅吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/80f56ba2f1a4d7e72953de189b9000a4.poster.avif?t=1768561756\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/80f56ba2f1a4d7e72953de189b9000a4.webm?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133830/extras/80f56ba2f1a4d7e72953de189b9000a4.mp4?t=1768561756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
